<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="jn1003a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="jn1" href="#jn1003">JN1: </a>  <a href="../../ff/unbs/jn1all.htm#jn1003a"> (NLI.2A) 3(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> <p class="set">I was not wearier where I lay <br>By frozen Tithon&apos;s side, to-night, <br>Than I am willing now to stay <br>And be part of your delight: <br>But I am urged by the Day, <br>Against my will, to bid you come away</p> <p class="diip"> <u>Ben Johnson</u></p> </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: <cite>The Works of Ben Jonson</cite>, ed. William Gifford (London: Nicol, 1816), <a href="https://archive.org/details/worksofbenjonson07jonsuoft/page/310/mode/2up" target="_blank">Vol. VII: &ldquo;The Vision of Delight&rdquo; p. 311</a>. </mm> </dd></dl>
